trans-unit.source: Represents a COM class that is described in a manifest.
trans-unit.target: 매니페스트에 설명 되어 있는 COM 클래스를 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ComClass"></xref> class.
Gets the class identifier (ClsId) for a <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ComClass"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 클래스 식별자 (ClsId)를 가져옵니다는 <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ComClass"> </xref> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> formatted in the pattern {xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx}, where the value of the GUID is represented as a series of lower-case hexadecimal digits in groups of 8, 4, 4, 4, and 12 digits and separated by hyphens.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.String>패턴 {xxxxxxxx xxxx-xxxx-.}, GUID의 값은 일련의 소문자 16 진수로 8, 4, 4, 4, 그룹 및 12 자리 숫자로 표시 하 고 하이픈으로 구분 된 형식입니다.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: An example of a return value is "{382c74c3-721d-4f34-80e5-57657b6cbc27}".
Gets the description of a <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ComClass"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 설명을 가져옵니다는 <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ComClass"> </xref> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: A description of the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ComClass"></xref> object.
Gets the programmatic identifier (ProgId) of a <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ComClass"></xref> object.
The programmatic identifier of the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ComClass"></xref> object.
Gets the threading model of a <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ComClass"></xref> object.
A string such as "Apartment".
Gets a value that is the identifier of the type library that contains type information about the class.
trans-unit.target: 클래스에 대 한 형식 정보를 포함 하는 형식 라이브러리의 식별자는 값을 가져옵니다.
